data.description: OPEN HOUSE TODAT Nov 5 from 1 pm to 4 pm    Seller offering 3.375% VA assumable to qualified buyers with agents getting a 2% commission!!!!    Beautiful 5 bedrooms, 3.5 baths, 3 car garage home located in the thriving community of Stevens Ranch! This elegant home features soaring ceilings, tile floors, formal dining + office, and an open kitchen/family room. The kitchen includes a huge granite island, butlers pantry, built-in stainless steel Whirlpool appliances, dark mocha cabinets. Huge game GAMEROOM/LOFT upstairs for the kids to game and watch movies. Stone/brick/stucco exterior, full sprinkler system, greenbelt lot, and covered backyard patio. Home automation + Community pool included.
